        <item>
            <title>【教学】免安装 AI 工具拉阔图片「Image Magic」   直倒横倒相片互换 + AI 填补内容</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/image-magic-outpainting/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=image-magic-outpainting</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/image-magic-outpainting/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 12:45:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Image Magic Outpainting]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285429</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>去年 Photoshop 推出了「生成扩张」功能喇，可以帮用家改变图片原生尺寸并以 AI 生成图片背景，小编试用过觉得非常实用，但不是人人都有订阅 Photoshop 服务，因此小编今天想和大家分享一个网上免费 AI 图片生成扩张工具。Image Magic 是一款免费网上工具，使用 AI 技术自动延展图片边界，补充缺失内容，并维持整体风格协调一致。有时如果将直度图片改为横度，左右会出现空白问题，此时可借由 Image Magic 的 Outpainting 技术自动延展图片内容至上下及两侧，并与原图风格天衣无缝地融合，呈现一气呵成的效果。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285430" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_4900-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_4900-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_4900-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_4900.jpg 651w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲拉大前为 1:1 比例</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image1-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image1-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image1-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可拉大为 16:9</p><h2>Image Magic (Outpainting) 网址：</h2><p><a href="https://huggingface.co/spaces/aiqcamp/imagemagic">https://huggingface.co/spaces/aiqcamp/imagemagic</a></p><p>开启网站后，你会看见下图画面，先将需要延伸的图片拖放至①上传，然后你可选择在②输入 Prompt（留空亦可），之后在③选择所需比例，目前支援 9:16、16:9、1:1，你也可以自订尺寸。确保一切设定无误之后，你就可以点击 ④ 拉大你的图片。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285432" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image_1-679x580.jpg" alt="" width="679" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image_1-679x580.jpg 679w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image_1.jpg 1053w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 679px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲网站主画面</p><h2>Step 1 上传图片</h2><p>首先将需要扩张的图片拖放至绿框。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285434" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image_2-682x580.jpg" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image_2-682x580.jpg 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image_2.jpg 1058w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
