            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>YouTube 一个动作背景播放教学，适用 iPhone Android 两平台毋须 Premium</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/youtube-background-play-music/tips-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=youtube-background-play-music</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/youtube-background-play-music/tips-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 11:20:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Android App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[youtube]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285437</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>官方 YouTube 网站只需要一个动作，就可以帮你将音乐设定在背景播放，毋须 YouTube Premium 帐户或者其他破解。以下就介绍 iOS, Android 两个平台的操作方法。</p><p>（由于软件经常改变其运作方式，以下操作方式有可能在未来用不到，想稳阵的话最好当然是课金 YouTube Premium 了）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285449" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010671403-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010671403-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010671403.jpg 832w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><h2>iOS 平台操作方式</h2><p>iOS 用家首先用 Google Chome 浏览器打开 YouTube 网站，并于此打开影片。有动态岛功能的 iPhone 可任意使用桌面版或流动版网站，如没有动态岛，请在 Chome 选项切换到桌面版网站。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285444" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-scaled.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p>返回主画面，此时音乐会暂停播放。请在 2 秒内按住动态岛，令它弹出，此时再按播放按钮，便可使音乐再次播放。现在你可离开 YouTube 网站，或在关闭荧幕时，都可在背景继续播放音乐。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285446" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-1-317x580.jpg" alt="" width="317" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-1-317x580.jpg 317w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-1-scaled.jpg 492w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 317px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲返回主画面后马上按住动态岛</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285447" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-2-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-2-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-2-scaled.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在动态岛通知按播放按钮便可</p><p>在关闭画面后，可在锁机画面的播放控制项中再次播放影片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285448" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-3-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-3-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010619h05-3-scaled.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p>（没有动态岛功能的 iPhone，请在切换桌面版网站后，关闭荧幕，并于荧幕的控制项中重新播放音乐便可）</p><h2>操作教学影片：</h2><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="ios" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1044277838?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/youtube-background-play-music/tips-2/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【CES 2025】磁吸 iPhone 数码相机手柄   Belkin PowerGrip 全新磁吸电池 + 快门按钮装置</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/belkin-powergrip/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=belkin-powergrip</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/belkin-powergrip/mobile-phone/phone-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 11:00:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手机配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Belkin PowerGrip]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285357</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Belkin 宣布推出全新 Stage PowerGrip 产品，这款磁吸电池组除了提供 iPhone 的额外电量，还能化身为数码相机风格的人体工学手柄，让手机摄影用家都可享受数码相机拍摄的质感。产品同时具备手机支架与外接有线充电功能，预计于 5 月上市，但定价尚未公布。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285359" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/cta003_powergrip_blu-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/cta003_powergrip_blu-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/cta003_powergrip_blu.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>PowerGrip 采用独特设计，连接手机后模样与传统相机相似，并支援蓝牙连接，让使用者可透过握把顶部的「快门按钮」操作 iOS 相机应用程式拍摄照片。装置内置 10,000mAh 电池，能为 iPhone 提供 7.5 瓦无线充电，并配有可伸缩 USB-C 传输线，支援其他装置充电。机身正面设有小型 LED 屏幕，显示剩余电量。</p><p>PowerGrip 将推出黑色、灰色、蓝色、黄色及深灰色等多款配色，提供更多选择，价格为 149.95 美元（约港币 HK$1,165）。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://eftm.com/2025/01/belkin-showcases-stage-powergrip-multi-purpose-smartphone-accessory-at-ces-2025-258612">EFTM</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
