        <item>
            <title>【CES 2025】Samsung 展示数码产品、电视 OLED 技术，超巨 18.1 吋折叠荧幕 + 4000 尼特 OLED 面板</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/samsung-oled-2025/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-oled-2025</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/samsung-oled-2025/wireless-home/audio-visual/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 09:56:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音产品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[OLED]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285408</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Samsung Display 于 CES 2025 发布一系列创新 OLED 技术，涵盖数码产品及汽车领域，展示未来显示技术的广阔应用。展示中最触目的可说是全球首款 18.1 吋折叠屏幕，为 IT 行业及车载显示方案带来多项突破。</p><h2><b>CES </b>展览重点<b></b>推动<b> OLED </b>技术应用范畴</h2><p>Samsung Display 于 CES 展出多款尖端 OLED 产品。除了平板电脑、手提电脑及显示器外，展品还包括针对汽车市场 OLED 显示器。该公司期望透过新型态荧幕设计，如滑动及多折叠屏幕，展示其领先于行业的技术优势。</p><p>其中首款 18.1 吋折叠显示屏可作为平板电脑、手提电脑及显示器使用，折叠后成为 13.1 吋触控屏幕手提电脑。这款产品进一步发展自 2022 年推出的 17.3 吋折叠面板。同场亦将展示多款创新产品，包括 Slidable Flex Duet（屏幕从 8.1 吋扩展至 12.4 吋）、Slidable Flex Solo（从 13 吋伸展至 17.3 吋）及垂直伸展的 Slidable Flex Vertical（屏幕可从 5.1 吋延伸至 6.7 吋）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285413" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jvghw50tdg_202501031-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jvghw50tdg_202501031-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jvghw50tdg_202501031-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285415" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/0m11pvbv78_202501031-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/0m11pvbv78_202501031-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/0m11pvbv78_202501031.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285416" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fvta37zl8t_202501031-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fvta37zl8t_202501031-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fvta37zl8t_202501031.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><b>QD-OLED </b>创新实现顶尖画质</h2><p>展览亦将推出新一代 QD-OLED 面板，透过先进技术及新有机材料，实现超过 4,000 尼特的峰值亮度，为目前市面上最亮的 OLED 电视屏幕。Samsung Display 同时展出专为游戏玩家及专业用户设计的高像素密度显示器，型号包括 27 吋、31.5 吋、34 吋及 49 吋。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285412" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ltccu5qxwx_202501031-694x437.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="437" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ltccu5qxwx_202501031-694x437.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ltccu5qxwx_202501031.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285417" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/cedjswgoue_202501031-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/cedjswgoue_202501031-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/cedjswgoue_202501031.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>「QD Jungle」为主题的媒体艺术空间，利用高亮度 QD-OLED 面板创造如置身森林的沉浸式体验，展示技术在色彩还原及影像细节上的卓越表现。</p><p>Samsung Display 亦将通过机械狗 OLEDog 为展览注入互动元素。OLEDog 配备 OLED 屏幕眼睛，表演敲击及踢击柔性面板等动作，展示 OLED 面板的卓越耐用性。</p><h2><b>OLED </b>技术助推车用显示市场</h2><p>Samsung Display 将展示专为汽车设计的创新 OLED 技术，包括提升安全与美观的多项新功能。例如嵌入屏幕下的摄像头（UPC）提升驾驶安全，同时保持内饰美观。另有弯曲式中央显示屏（CID），可根据驾驶模式调整形态，提升驾驶体验及空间利用率。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285414" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/byjhzvkmr8_202501031-694x469.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/byjhzvkmr8_202501031-694x469.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/byjhzvkmr8_202501031-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Real Black 抬头显示器（HUD）透过嵌入 OLED 技术于挡风玻璃，展示驾驶资讯，实现模组减重及黑色表现完美融合，提供更高内饰设计自由度。</p><p>资料来源：Samsung</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/06/samsung-oled-2025/wireless-home/audio-visual/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
