            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285398</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>LG 在 CES 2025 展示出推出第二代便携式电视 LG StanbyME 2，设计让用户能轻松携带或直接安装于墙面。此款产品延续了趣味性和实用性的结合，吸引了不少科技爱好者的关注。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285401 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652935-347x580.jpg" alt="" width="347" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652935-347x580.jpg 347w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652935.jpg 539w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 347px" /></p><p>新款 StanbyME 2 采用 27 吋 16:9 萤幕，并提升至 1440p 解像度，相较上一代的 1080p，画质表现进一步改良。同时电池续航时间从前代的 3.5 小时延长至 4 小时，为用户提供更多灵活使用空间。电视甚至可配合孭带，可便携带出户外使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285402 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652947-383x580.jpg" alt="" width="383" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652947-383x580.jpg 383w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010652947.jpg 595w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 383px" /></p><p>在配件方面，LG 引入一款类似于大型 iPad 的折叠式保护套，增加产品便携性及多用途应用场景。此外，StanbyME 2 新增两个 USB-C 接口，让用户可以连接视像镜头等配件，进一步提升装置的多功能性。遥控方面，则采用了磁吸设计，令使用体验更为便捷。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_90111"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/P45K999opDA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P45K999opDA">The Verge</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
