            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285341</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>德国科技企业 Bosch 在 CES 2025 展会中展示全新 AI 智能婴儿床「Revol」，内置多重感应器，能即时追踪及监测婴儿的心率、呼吸频率与周围环境数据，为父母提供详细报告及即时提醒，冀能减少育儿焦虑。目前这款产品暂未公布确实推出日期，Bosch 计划 2026 年于中国市场率先发售，稍后才登陆美国市场。</p><h3></h3><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285346" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/d4fc6cc0cbd511efaa7f-1-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/d4fc6cc0cbd511efaa7f-1-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/d4fc6cc0cbd511efaa7f-1.jpeg 960w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Revol 婴儿床外观与现有智能婴儿床 Snoo 相似，采用透气网状墙壁设计，并具备自动摇动功能。Revol 创新引入垂直升降摇动模式，床垫会模仿升降机缓慢上升及下降，进一步舒缓婴儿情绪。此外 Revol 配备内建视像监控系统，能向父母提供实时影像画面。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285366 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010641132-694x424.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="424" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010641132-694x424.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010641132.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>床架上延伸出的手臂内藏多组感应器，可监测婴儿周边环境，包括温度、湿度及空气质素等数据。当中使用毫米波雷达感应技术，能精准测量婴儿心率及呼吸频率，并将数据同步至家长手机应用程式，实现随时随地掌握健康报告的需求。</p><h3></h3><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285347" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ebe332b0cbd611efbfff-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ebe332b0cbd611efbfff-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ebe332b0cbd611efbfff.jpeg 960w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>作为 2025 年新产品，Revol 亦具备 AI 技术，透过电脑视觉检测婴儿身边是否有毯子或毛绒玩具等物件靠近脸部，并即时发出安全提醒，减少意外窒息风险，呼应美国儿科学会对婴儿睡眠环境安全的建议。</p><h3></h3><p>Bosch 表示，Revol 售价预计约 1,200 美元（约港币 HK$9,360），还会推出多款配件，如可将婴儿床转换成尿布更换台或书桌，延长产品使用寿命。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_33883"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YeqqxAyYQm8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/smart-home/boschs-ai-enabled-bassinet-tracks-everything-youd-ever-want-to-know-about-your-babys-sleep-025258549.html">Engadget</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
